data.description: AGENT BONUS..... Seller must relocate out of state.   This beautiful brick home  is 2,337 sf, 4 br, 2 ba Adams home sits on almost half an acre and backs up to a 30 acre pecan farm. The living room is open to the kitchen which has been updated with a farm sink, classic countertops, new lighting and new flooring through out. The floor plan is open and has high ceilings.  This home is mechanically sound and has Solar Panels   This home offers a perfect location near Whiting Field and great shopping. The backyard is fully fenced and is perfect for your family pets and playtime,  If you have a family member in need this home is wheel chair accessible and friendly.  This garage is big enough for a small 17' boat
